This paper involves natural language processing techniques such as sentiment analysis and text processing to recommend personalized food items to users. Therefore, it is most likely to belong to the Information Retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category. Additionally, it also involves machine learning techniques such as recommender systems, which are commonly found in sub-categories such as Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Cybernetics (cs.CY).
